SOC Home Lab Workflow Architecture

Overview

This SOC Home Lab demonstrates a modern Blue Team and Security Operations Center (SOC) environment using enterprise-grade open-source security tools.

The lab focuses on:

- Network security monitoring
- Threat detection and response
- SIEM log analysis
- Threat intelligence sharing
- Security automation
- Alerting and incident response
- DNS filtering and network segmentation


